        "1.3.6": "<p>Fix for a problem which occurs when DISALLOW_FILE_EDIT is set true.<\/p>",
        "1.3.5": "<p>Slim Maintenance Mode now supports the WP Fastest Cache plugin.<\/p>",
        "1.3.4": "<p>Opened Slim Maintenance Mode to the WordPress Translate community.<\/p>",
        "1.3.3": "<p>Slim Maintenance Mode now supports the WP-Rocket Cache plugin and provides a better way to get quicker to the plugin deactivation from the note in the backend.<\/p>",
        "1.3.1": "<p>Slim Maintenance Mode is now available in Russian.<\/p>",
        "1.3": "<p>Slim Maintenance Mode is now available in Brazilian Portuguese and comes with a bug fix for better loading translated strings.<\/p>",
        "1.2": "<p>Slim Maintenance Mode is now available in French and Spanish.<\/p>"
